+%% Inicis NOTI server callback
+sequenceDiagram
+    participant PG as Inicis NOTI server
+    participant Edge as /pg_module/pg_db_update.php
+    participant Verifier as pg_db_update()
+    participant Ledger as Ledger & member tables
+    PG->>Edge: POST P_TID, P_STATUS, P_OID
+    Edge->>Edge: Check PG IP allowlist
+    Edge->>Verifier: Invoke inicis branch (P_STATUS == 00)
+    Verifier->>Ledger: Update in_check + entitlements
+    Ledger-->>Verifier: Success
+    Verifier-->>PG: Echo "OK"
+    Edge-->>PG: HTTP 200
+
+%% Inicis standard return (PC)
+sequenceDiagram
+    participant Browser as Customer browser
+    participant PGStd as Inicis std API
+    participant Edge as /pg_module/pg_db_update.php
+    participant Verifier as pg_db_update()
+    participant Ledger as Ledger & member tables
+    Browser->>Edge: POST resultCode, authToken, merchantData
+    Edge->>PGStd: Verify signature & auth via HttpClient
+    PGStd-->>Edge: resultMap + TotPrice
+    Edge->>Verifier: Run pg_db_update() on success
+    Verifier->>Ledger: Apply order fulfilment
+    Ledger-->>Verifier: Success
+    Verifier-->>Browser: Script redirect/close popup
+
+%% LG Uplus (dacom)
+sequenceDiagram
+    participant Browser as Customer browser
+    participant Edge as /pg_module/pg_db_update.php
+    participant LG as XPayClient (LG Uplus)
+    participant Verifier as pg_db_update()
+    participant Ledger as Ledger & member tables
+    Browser->>Edge: POST CST_PLATFORM, LGD_PAYKEY
+    Edge->>LG: PaymentByKey TX (server-to-server)
+    LG-->>Edge: LGD_RESPCODE, LGD_AMOUNT, LGD_TID
+    Edge->>Edge: Compare amount with session PAYREQ_MAP
+    Edge->>Verifier: Invoke pg_db_update() on match
+    Verifier->>Ledger: Update in_check & options
+    Ledger-->>Verifier: Success
+    Verifier-->>Browser: Redirect to success page
+
+%% AllTheGate (PC/mobile)
+sequenceDiagram
+    participant Browser as Customer browser / SDK
+    participant Edge as /pg_module/pg_db_update.php
+    participant AGS as AGS library
+    participant Verifier as pg_db_update()
+    participant Ledger as Ledger & member tables
+    Browser->>Edge: POST tracking data + amounts
+    Edge->>AGS: startPay()/approve()
+    AGS-->>Edge: rSuccYn == y, OrdNo, Amt
+    Edge->>Edge: Compare Amt with session value
+    Edge->>Verifier: pg_db_update()
+    Verifier->>Ledger: Apply packages/points
+    Ledger-->>Verifier: Success
+    Verifier-->>Browser: JS redirect / success page
+
+%% Daoupay notify
+sequenceDiagram
+    participant PG as Daoupay notifier
+    participant Edge as /pg_module/pg_db_update.php
+    participant Verifier as pg_db_update()
+    participant Ledger as Ledger & member tables
+    PG->>Edge: GET ORDERNO, AMOUNT, RESERVEDINDEX1
+    Edge->>Edge: Validate PG IP range and amount via pg_jangboo_chk
+    Edge->>Verifier: Invoke pg_db_update()
+    Verifier->>Ledger: Set in_check, credit entitlements
+    Ledger-->>Verifier: Success
+    Verifier-->>PG: XML <RESULT>SUCCESS</RESULT>
+    Edge-->>PG: HTTP 200
